This is the README file for RTx::Report, an interactive SQL
report generator based on DBIx::SearchBuilder.

Please type "perldoc RTx::Report" after installation to see
the module usage information.

* Installation

RTx::Report the standard perl module install process:

cpansign -v		# see SIGNATURE for details
perl Makefile.PL
make			# or 'nmake' on Win32; see notes below
make test
make install

